data.title: Great Sushi
data.text: This place has become a regular stop. I love this place. I finally just started letting the Sushi chef surprise me with his choice. I have never had anything I did not like. I generally just ask for a forty dollar order to go. Lots of food and lots of variety. Highly recommend this place.

data.title: Fresh Food Clean Place
data.text: We dined in the first night and liked it so much we called in an order for pick up the 2nd night.  Everything is made fresh, the place is very clean with great service and gluetin free options.
